copic follow-up. Importantly, we find\nthat by using either the SALT2 or the wavelet feature sets with a BDT\nalgorithm, accurate classification is possible purely from light curve data,\nwithout the need for any redshift information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2016 21:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2016 18:07:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Sep 2016 17:06:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-08"}
